app.use(helmet());
// Adds: X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, Strict-Transport-Security,
//        Content-Security-Policy, X-XSS-Protection, and more
```

### 5. No Rate Limiting (OWASP A04: Insecure Design)

Both endpoints are wide open to brute-force and denial-of-service attacks. There is no throttling of any kind.

